data.description: Fantastic 4 bedroom 2 bathroom bi-level.  Conveniently located in south Fargo this home has so much to offer including new carpet, and fresh paint.  The tile floor in entryway flows to upper level and into kitchen, and living room. Upstairs bath features upgraded tile surround with custom built-in shelves.   The beautiful Alder cabinets and granite  countertops pair perfectly with the stainless steel appliances.  Cathedral ceilings and recessed lighting keep make the space light and bright.  Outside enjoy a maintenance free deck and fully fenced yard. In the lower level living room has high end laminate flooring and the bathroom has a full tile shower with floor heat.  Plus don't forget the three stall garage! Schedule your showing today!
